His snake staff began to glow, and green lightning crackled around it.
Rajah let out a roar and lunged at Jafar. Jafar waved his staff, and in
midair. Rajah was transformed into a kitten. As Rajah landed softly
on his paws, Jafar glared at Jasmine and Aladdin. "Take a look at
your precious Prince Ali—or should we say, Alad-din!"
A bolt of light shot from the staff. It surrounded Aladdin and Abu.
Instantly Abu became a monkey again. Aladdin's robe, slippers, and
