Aladdin and Abu suddenly levitated off the ground and into the open
window of a narrow tower. In an instant, the tower rocketed over the
horizon. The carpet sped after it.
Jasmine watched in horror as the tower vanished over the horizon.
The genie sadly turned away.
With a devious laugh, Jafar shouted, "At last! Agra-bah is mine!"
